</p>
<p>(Ghana); Copenhagen (Denmark); Graz (Austria); Gwangju (Republic of Korea); Kaohsiung (Taiwan 
</p>
<p>Province of China); Kati (Mali); Korogocho (Kenya); Mexico city (Mexico); Mogale (South Africa); 
</p>
<p>Montreal (Canada); Nagpur (India); Porto Alegre (Brazil); Prince George County (United States); 
</p>
<p>Saint-Denis (France); Sakai (Japan); Thies (Senegal); Utrecht (the Netherlands); Victoria (Australia). 
</p>
