</p>
<p> 32 The Habitat International Coalition and its Housing and Land Rights Network have worked over the 
</p>
<p>past decade to promote and develop the definition of &#8220;the right to the city&#8221;. 
</p>
<p> 33 Available from www.ifrc.org/docs/idrl/945EN.pdf. 
</p>
<p> 34 Available from http://ville.montreal.qc.ca/portal/page?_pageid=3036,3377687&amp;_dad=portal&amp;_ 
</p>
<p>schema=PORTAL. 
</p>
